Package: mate-session-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         mate-settings-daemon,
         mate-panel,
         mate-window-manager,
         mate-file-manager,
         mate-polkit,
         dbus-x11,
         upower
Description: The MATE Session Manager
 This package contains a session that can be started from a display
 manager such as MDM. It will load all necessary applications for a
 full-featured user session.
 .
 The session manager also features the ability to save a running session
 an restore it later.
 .
 This version is configured to start the MATE 2 desktop, based on the
 MATE panel.

